text: Tsvetan Donchev (, born 6 July 1953) is a Bulgarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bulgaria Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
